snippet.title: Half-Life 2: Survivor Ver2.0 - Mission Mode Gameplay
snippet.description:
Gameplay footage of Mission Mode in Half-Life 2: Survivor Ver2.0 played on the PC, featuring the infamous Zombie House mission. Actual gameplay begins at 2:00.

Endless gratitude goes to ben1066 for fixing the binaries. Your generosity will not be forgotten through all eternity.
